[8:52 PM] Oliver Kim: I think I am going to kill everyone in the office tomorrow. I am not even sure why I am even writing this down here. But if you are reading this do not come into the office unless you want to die along side with me (which I will be honored). Tomorrow will bring glory to my family.
[8:52 PM] Oliver Kim: The office bathroom is becoming something ridiculous. There is literally poop that is smeared along the walls. The toilets are turning yellow from all the pee that has been sprayed on it. How do I even go poop if I can't even sit on the toilet. I have to walk to the restaurant across the street to even use the restroom. Toilets should not be turning yellow. Toilets should be clean.
